@startuml US-08
title US-08 View Order Details

actor User
boundary "Web UI" as UI
control "OrderController" as OC
control "OrderService" as OS
database "OrderItemRepository" as OIR
database "GameRepository" as GR

User -> UI: Click Order ID
UI -> OC: GET /orders/{orderId}
OC -> OS: getOrderDetails(orderId)

OS -> OIR: findByOrderId(orderId)
OIR --> OS: items(gameId, purchasePrice)

loop for each item
  OS -> GR: findById(gameId)
  GR --> OS: gameTitle
end

OS --> OC: items(gameTitle, purchasePrice)
OC --> UI: 200 OK + details
UI --> User: Render order items
@enduml
